        section.section.section--questions
          .container
            h2.section__title.section__title--blocked.section__title--question Frequently Asked Questions
            .questions
              .questions__block.questions__block--one
                span.questions__block-title How much does Ghost cost?
                p.questions__block-text Phantom is currently listed for $300.00 USD with a 6 month license duration* License keys will be granted a 7-day grace period upon expiration to renew their Phantom. Failure to renew will lead to permanent termination of the license keys.
              .questions__block.questions__block--two
                span.questions__block-title Will I need to pay for updates?
                p.questions__block-text All purchases of Phantom include membership for 180 days. After your license expires you will have to purchase a license extension to continue to use Ghost. Renewals are currently priced at $150 USD.
              ul.questions__desc.questions__desc--one
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title Is there a Discord/Slack for customers?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text A discord is provided to customers upon purchasing Phantom, we provide support and suggested release help. Please keep in mind, this discord does NOT have any relation to your purchase of Phantom. Losing access to discord is not our responsibility.
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title When is Phantom releasing again?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text Restocks are currently random but we do announce via our twitter page @GhostAIO, be sure to follow us and turn on post notification.
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title What countries are supported?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text We support all regions shipped to by our current list of supported retailers. This list is subjected to change in the future as we work on adding more countries to the supported list!
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title Can we do a group buy?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text Due to the format of releasing copies, we will be accepting groups buys by application only here.
              ul.questions__desc.questions__desc--two
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title What sites does Ghost Support?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text We currently support the following: FootLocker US/EU/CA, YeezySupply, Supreme US/EU, Adidas, FootAction, Champs Sports, EastBay, Finish Line, JD Sports, Dick's Sporting Goods, Hibbett Sports, JimmyJazz, WellGosh, Titolo, Overkill Shop
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title Acceptable payment methods
                  p.questions__desc-item-text To purchase Phantom, we utilize Shopify’s payment gateway which includes both credit cards and PayPal.
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title I’ve missed a drop. How can I get a copy?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text Although restocks are random, we will try our website to vary the release times in order to accommodate for all regions. We will NOT backdoor copies.
                li.questions__desc-item
                  +image('content/question2.png', 'questions__desc-icon')
                  span.questions__desc-item-title What operating systems are supported?
                  p.questions__desc-item-text Phantom supports both Windows (64-Bit) and Mac OS (10.13 and later).
